    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drop into the wildest Brawler arena where you and your squad can flex those trigger fingers! Neon Knights is an action-packed, neon-drenched shooter that’s all about local &amp; online multiplayer madness. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What’s your Knight?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow – Snipe ‘em with precision!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Machine – Spray and pray!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blade – Use that cutting edge technology!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wall – Tank it like a boss!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcane – Make it rain! (with bullets, I mean)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against your friends or a horde of bots in dynamic Neon Arenas. Every time you burn out, you respawn harder, faster, stronger, brighter! Stack glorious powerups ‘til you’re a glowing juggernaut. Last Knight standing? That’s the goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo queue? Squad up? Local couch co-op or online brawls? Neon Knights supports it all - play with your friends locally, play with some here and some there, play all online. We made this game as an homage to the best of days gone by - playing with your friends any way you’d like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s time to light up that scoreboard, bury your rivals, and rule the Neon void tonight!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<strong>*</strong>, 日语<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
